item.description:
FUN filled evening - great food, raffle and entertainment....

All proceeds will benefit BV Cats, Inc., a local non-profit organization dedicated to reducing the cat population while improving the lives of stray and feral cats in Blackstone Valley and surrounding areas.

When: May 12, 2012

Where: The Italian Workingmen's Club, 947 Diamond Hill Road, Woonsocket RI 02895

Time: 5 pm - 10 pm

Tickets are $15 and can be purchased in advance by calling Doreen at 401-323-2663 OR Lo at 401-263-3088
